title: Sportanlage Leitawies
text: Sportanlange Leitawies is a <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="stadium">stadium</a> in <a href="Triesenberg">Triesenberg</a>, <a href="Liechtenstein">Liechtenstein</a>. It is the home ground of <a href="FC%20Triesenberg">FC Triesenberg</a> and has a capacity of 800 made up of 400 seats and 400 standing places.
